title: Static Analysis

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

com.fit.caloriecounter.permission.C2D_ME.description: Allows the application to receive push notifications.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.BROADCAST_STICKY.description: Allows an application to send sticky broadcasts, which remain after the broadcast ends. Malicious applications can make the phone slow or unstable by causing it to use too much memory.

android.permission.MOUNT_UNMOUNT_FILESYS.description: Allows the application to mount and unmount file systems for removable storage.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

manifest_analysis.title:
Broadcast Receiver (com.google.android.gcm.GCMBroadcastReceiver) is Protected by a permission, but the protection level of the permission should be checked.
Permission: com.google.android.c2dm.permission.SEND
[android:exported=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: A Broadcast Receiver is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. It is protected by a permission which is not defined in the analysed application. As a result, the protection level of the permission should be checked where it is defined. If it is set to normal or dangerous, a malicious application can request and obtain the permission and interact with the component. If it is set to signature, only applications signed with the same certificate can obtain the permission.

playstore_details.title: Fit Bites
playstore_details.description:
"Your body is a pure reflection of what you eat. If you want to look fit and stay healthy the key is to eat healthy!"
Looking for some healthy food options? Need a low fat rice dish? Confused because you don't want to ditch your diet?
It is known to everyone that to lose weight - 30% contribution comes from exercise and 70% role is played by your food choices. Does it mean that you would be eating tasteless food for whole your life?
Here comes a savior app which will help you to save your time and efforts to find the perfect recipe to support your weight loss regime. You would no longer be required to flip through various cookbooks to eat something delectable yet low in calories. With this amazing app you would never experience bland, boring food again on your diet regime. The simple trick is to enjoy the flavors of your favorite dish by using healthier options in its preparation. Along with hand-picked ingredient list, step-by-step direction to make the dishes, all the featured recipes have nutritional information too, so you’ll know how many calories, carbs, fats, proteins, etc. you’ll consume per serving.

With this amazing recipes application you can:
- Search recipe from the huge collection.
- A recipe box to save your favorite recipes.
- Share recipes with your friends.
- New recipes added on daily basis.
So, enjoy these healthy recipes with your friends and family and don't forget to share your comments in the reviews section. **Bon appetite**!

Whats Special
● Helps to achieve desired results with your favorite food!
● Fast & Smooth Performance
● Clear & Intuitive design
● Punch of animations 
● Phone Resource friendly

Ads
This Smart App is brought to you for free, thus please consider that it contains in-app purchases to Remove Ads!

Disclaimer
This application is based on generic information. In case of any special ailment or disease, consult your physician/dietitian before consumption. 

Note
Internet connection is needed to run this app in a smooth manner, and since this app is free, we support ourselves by showing non-intrusive ads.

Support: contactdorange@gmail.com
For any kind of confusion, simply write to us & we would happily resolve your issues in a quick friendly manner. Kindly do not leave us negative stars, we're here to help :)
